    <mxCell id="2" value="Unsupervised Concept Discovery &amp; Post-Hoc Semantic Grounding  (Pillars 1 &amp; 3)" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=15;fontStyle=1;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="10" y="10" width="1160" height="38" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="3" value="Clustering is identical across domains  ·  Labeling mechanism differs  ·  No concept labels required at training time" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;fontStyle=2;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="10" y="50" width="1160" height="22" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="4" value="IMAGE DOMAIN" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#1565C0;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#1565C0;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="10" y="78" width="560" height="30" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="5" value="LAB DOMAIN" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#2E7D32;fontColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#2E7D32;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="600" y="78" width="560" height="30" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="6" value="Feature Input
DINO patch features  [N_patches × 1,152-dim]
(after FG masking — ~300 patches per image)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="118" width="540" height="60" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="7" value="PCA Dimensionality Reduction
1,152-dim  →  128-dim  (retains ≈90% variance)
Spatial coordinates (row/col) appended" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="188" width="540" height="55" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="8" value="Gaussian Mixture Model  (GMM)
30 clusters  ·  full covariance
Soft cluster assignments → hard labels
Spatial smoothing: majority-vote per patch neighbourhood" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="253" width="540" height="70" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="9" value="Cluster Visualisation
For each cluster: display representative patch grids
Color-overlay on original image
Streamlit UI  (labeling/image_cluster_labeler.py)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="333" width="540" height="65" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="10" value="Human SME Labeling
Domain expert views patch grids
→ assigns semantic name per cluster
e.g.  cluster 4 → &quot;cat_ear&quot;
       cluster 9 → &quot;wheel_rim&quot;
       cluster 17 → &quot;wing_feather&quot;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="408" width="540" height="80" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="11" value="labels.json
{&quot;4&quot;: &quot;cat_ear&quot;,  &quot;9&quot;: &quot;wheel_rim&quot;,  ...}
Unlabeled clusters ignored in downstream steps" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="498" width="540" height="55" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="12" value="Concept Vectors
Mean DINO feature of all patches in labeled cluster
One 384-dim vector per named concept" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="20" y="563" width="540" height="55" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="13" value="Concept Activation Scores
score[image, concept] = fraction of image patches
assigned to that concept cluster
