    <mxCell id="21" value="Feature Input
PSFTT panel-patch features  [N_records × 3 × 384-dim]
One 384-dim vector per clinical panel per record" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="610" y="118" width="540" height="60" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="22" value="PCA per Panel
384-dim  →  20-dim per panel
Clustering done independently per panel" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dae8fc;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="610" y="188" width="540" height="55" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="23" value="Per-Panel GMM  (3 × 10 = 30 clusters total)
CBC panel: 10 clusters
BMP panel: 10 clusters    Lipid panel: 10 clusters
Soft assignments → hard labels per record" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="610" y="253" width="540" height="70" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="24" value="Cluster Deviation Profile Generation
For each cluster: compute centroid in original lab space
Format as signed deviation from clinical normal range
e.g.  WBC ↑1.8σ  ·  HGB ↓2.1σ  ·  MCV ↓1.4σ
Streamlit UI  (labeling/lab_cluster_labeler.py)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#d5e8d4;strokeColor=#82b366;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="610" y="333" width="540" height="75" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="25" value="LLM Clinical Advisor
LLM reads deviation profile
→ suggests clinical concept label
→ lists differential diagnoses
e.g.  &quot;CBC pattern consistent with iron-deficiency anaemia&quot;
       differentials: [thalassaemia, chronic disease anaemia]" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontStyle=1;fontSize=9;align=center;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="610" y="418" width="540" height="80" as="geometry" /></mxCell>
    <mxCell id="26" value="Human Clinician Validation
Clinic expert reviews LLM suggestion
→ accepts / corrects label
→ records confidence score
